quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  7,131,"Olwa obulayi bwabolelanga, baboolanga mbu; “Buno ni shichira efwe.” Ne obubii nibubetsela, nibalola okusubilo khu Musa nende abali ninaye. Toto okusubilo kwenyu oko kuli ewa Nyasaye (sichila amabii kabu), halali abaanji mubo shibamanyile tawe."
  7,132,"Nibaboola mbu; “Kata nokhwitsila orie nende eshimanyisio shiosishiosi mbu okhuloche nasho, shikhulakhusuubila tawe.”"
  7,133,"Mana nikhubarumila imbumbuyeka, nende tsisiche, nende tsikhungu, nende amashele, nende amalasile; okhuba ebimanyisio ebia habulafu. Mana nibakhola obufuru, ne nibaba Abandu abamabii."
  7,134,"Ne olwa eshinyasio shabanyoola, baboola mbu; “Ewe Musa, khusabile Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khu kalia akayakhulaka. Nokhurusiliao eshinyasio shino, toto khulakhusuubila, ne toto khulakhulekhulila Abana ba Israili otsie ninabo.”"
  7,135,"Ne ngala khwabayiniliao eshinyasio okhula ebise bindi, nibachaka okhufunaka indache."
  7,136,"Mana nikhubarunga imongo yeshinyasio, nikhubasishia munyanza shichila bakatsula ebimanyisio biefu, nende okhubula khwabu nabio oluchendo."
  7,137,"Mana nikhuchelamia abandu balolekhananga abateshele, ebukwe nende mumbo weshialo ewakhwarayo tsikhabi. Mana likhuwa lilayi lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi nilileng’ana khubaana ba Israili khulwa okhwisumilisia khwabu. Mana nikhusishia aka Firaun yakholanga nende Abandu bebe, nende bilia ebia bombakhanga."